# Iteration 4 — Backlog Research & Gate

## Work Done

Classified task as CODE TASK. Researched codebase, wrote research.md/criteria.md/todo.md, implemented all changes, and moved card to in-progress.

### Key findings
- `shipped → in-progress` transition was absent from `gates.ts` — blocked by "invalid transition" error
- `fileAttached()` in `gates.ts` preferred relative paths over absolute ones — `existsSync("criteria.md")` fails server-side
- Move API had no `note` field — couldn't attach reopen reason to workLog
- CardPanel had no state-change UI

### Files changed
- `apps/board/src/worker/gates.ts` — fixed `fileAttached` to prefer absolute paths; added `shipped → in-progress` (always allowed)
- `apps/board/src/app/api/cards/[id]/move/schema.ts` — added optional `note: string` field
- `apps/board/src/app/api/cards/[id]/move/route.ts` — appends `note` to workLog via `updateCard` after move
- `apps/board/src/components/CardPanel.tsx` — added `ReopenDialog` component + "Reopen" button visible only on shipped cards
- Same changes applied to live server at `/Users/michaeloneal/am/apps/board/` for dev server hot-reload

